This file is for download of the latest radar data and the reanalysis CPC files. It is not automated. 
The reanalysis CPC files are only available 8 days later an only as the values at full hours. This script takes this into account. 
In rare cases, if the reanalysis file has other quality flag in the filname, you will have more than 24h files per day. 
There please always use the newer file with the higher quality flag in the filename. 
